		<div id="post-2" class="post-2 page type-page status-publish hentry">

						
			<div class="entry-content">
				<div style="margin: 0 35px 0 35px;">
<blockquote><p>Welcome to Bondloc &#8211; a UK based manufacturer of industrial adhesives &#038; sealants, offering high quality and performance products to its global distribution and OEM partners</p></blockquote>
<div class="ezcol ezcol-one-quarter">
<h1 align="center">About Us</h1>
<p>Bondloc UK Ltd is a British manufacturer of adhesives and sealants based in Bewdley, Worcestershire.</p>
<p>The company was formed 25 years ago and supply into all areas of industry including engineering, automotive, marine, heavy plant and agriculture.</p>
<p>Our mission is to provide our customers with a service and a product range second to none aiming to make Bondloc the adhesive product of choice.</div><div class="ezcol ezcol-one-quarter">
<h1 align="center">Why Bondloc</h1>
<p>Bondloc are ISO 9001 quality approved, WRAS approved for potable Water, and NATO approved, and our extensive and ever expanding product range underlines our commitment to meet the demands of our customers.</p>
<p>At Bondloc we are committed to providing our customers with high quality products and this is evident not only in our manufacturing process but also in the quality of our service and our approach to our customers needs.</div><div class="ezcol ezcol-one-quarter">
<h1 align="center">Private Label</h1>
<p>Bondloc offers private label formulations for a wide variety of customers interested in marketing products under their own label.</p>
<p>Our team are dedicated to fulfilling your requirements for quality adhesives, sealants, &#038; cleaners. We address every aspect of research and development, production, quality control, packaging and labelling to ensure regulatory compliance.</p>
<p>Our goal is customer satisfaction.</div><div class="ezcol ezcol-one-quarter ezcol-last">
<h1 align="center">Latest News</h1>
<div><a class="twitter-timeline" data-height="350" width="250" data-link-color="#cb2322" href="https://twitter.com/BondlocUK?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">Tweets by BondlocUK</a> <script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div>
</div><div class="ezcol-divider"></div></p>
